"{\"uid\": \"hollywoodreporter.com-news-general-news-olympics-drag-performance-last-supper-backlash-conservatives-1235960103\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe for full access to The Hollywood Reporter  Subscribe for full access to The Hollywood Reporter  Some say the performance featuring drag queens and dancers during the Opening Ceremony in Paris resembled the Leonardo da Vinci portrait.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.911609073134e-58, \"text\": \"The Hollywood Reporter\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\"}, {\"begin\": 82, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.911609073134e-58, \"text\": \"The Hollywood Reporter\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.02641098557304e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ByCarly Thomas  Associate Editor  TheOpening Ceremony at the 2024 Paris Olympic Gamesfeatured numerous performances, but there was one in particular that drew mixed reactions, including outrage from conservative leaders.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9407076262686681, \"rank\": 0.06290834435474942, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the four-hour ceremony on Friday, drag queens and dancers at one point struck poses along a long table as a person painted sparkly blue, singing in French, was resting on a dinner platter in front.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people quickly took to social media to say that the image resembled Leonardo da Vinci'sThe Last Supperportrait of Jesus Christ and his 12 apostles before he was crucified.Related StoriesNewsWhite House Launches \\\"Media Offender of the Week\\\" Section on Its WebsiteNewsRyan Lizza Claims Olivia Nuzzi Would Share \\\"Opposition Research\\\" With Robert F. Kennedy Jr.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4028078379121321e-28, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999973365448, \"rank\": 2.6632525184757182e-09, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Reporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.402046249160894e-20, \"text\": \"F.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Reporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Reporter\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"score\": 0.9999999988644959, \"rank\": 1.1349907459545227e-09, \"text\": \"Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The table later transformed into a catwalk for models and drag queens to showcase Paris' fashion scene.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.02641098557304e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"House Speaker Mike Johnsonwroteon X (formerly Twitter) following the performance, \\\"Last night's mockery of theLast Supperwas shocking and insulting to Christian people around the world who watched the opening ceremony of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1141, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speaker_of_the_United_States_House_of_Representatives\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3514637126931215e-14, \"text\": \"House Speaker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speaker_of_the_United_States_House_of_Representatives\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speaker_of_the_United_States_House_of_Representatives\"}, {\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9995752891324327, \"rank\": 0.00042488721619740095, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The war on our faith and traditional values knows no bounds today.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we know that truth and virtue will always prevail.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The light shines in the darkness, and the darkness has not overcome it.'\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(John 1:5)\\\"  Donald Trump\\u00a0later toldFox Newshost Laura Ingraham that he thought the moment \\\"was a disgrace.\\\"\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.276869746526681e-14, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.830897016443693e-31, \"text\": \"Laura Ingraham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French far-right politician, Marion Mar\\u00e9chal, denounced the performance on social media,writing, \\\"To all the Christians of the world who are watching the Paris 2024 ceremony and felt insulted by this drag queen parody of the Last Supper, know that it is not France that is speaking but a left-wing minority ready for any provocation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_far-right_movements_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French far-right\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_far-right_movements_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_far-right_movements_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1716, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"score\": 0.9999998162447978, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marion Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\"}, {\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9803558208778574, \"rank\": 0.013884961821858553, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.71908306987457e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993994315534153, \"rank\": 0.0004581123210912417, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full Housealum Candace Cameron Bure also expressed her disappointment in anInstagram video, saying, \\\"To watch such an incredible and wonderful event that's gonna take place over the next two weeks and see the opening ceremonies completely blaspheme and mock the Christian faith with their interpretation of theLast Supperwas disgusting.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Candace Cameron Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 2054, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"score\": 0.7702581713258163, \"rank\": 0.2982660064203002, \"text\": \"Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 2285, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9995752891324327, \"rank\": 0.00042488721619740095, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it made me so sad.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And someone said, 'You should not be sad.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You should be mad about it.'\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am like, 'Trust me.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes me mad.'\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am more sad, because I am sad for souls.\\\"\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Harrison Butker, the Kansas City Chiefs kicker who faced backlash earlier this year after giving acontroversial commencement\\u00a0speech, also quoted the Bibleon Xafter the ceremony: \\\"'Be not deceived, God is not mocked.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2547, \"end\": 2562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harrison_Butker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Harrison Butker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harrison_Butker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harrison_Butker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For what things a man shall sow, those also shall he reap.\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For he that soweth in his flesh, of the flesh also shall reap corruption.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he that soweth in the spirit, of the spirit shall reap life everlasting.'\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Galatians 6:7-8.\\\"\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epistle_to_the_Galatians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.728027840915898e-23, \"text\": \"Galatians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epistle_to_the_Galatians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epistle_to_the_Galatians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the official X account for the Olympic Games shared photos of the performance, noting that it was meant to reference the Greek god Dionysus, notThe Last Supper.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3123, \"end\": 3128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9963779473162386, \"rank\": 0.0036279168679230517, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.562192874958902e-30, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings,\\\" the photo's caption read.\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9963779473162386, \"rank\": 0.0036279168679230517, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 3201, \"end\": 3209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.562192874958902e-30, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Jolly, the artistic director of the Olympics Opening Ceremony, also defended the performance during anews conferenceSaturday when asked about the criticism, saying he wanted to display \\\"inclusion.\\\"\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3304, \"end\": 3310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9407076262686681, \"rank\": 0.06290834435474942, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 3356, \"end\": 3372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.5942548122493106, \"rank\": 0.37745100774056506, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we want to include everyone and not exclude anyone, questions are raised,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our subject was not to be subversive.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We never wanted to be subversive.\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to talk about diversity.\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Diversity means being together.\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to include everyone, as simple as that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued, \\\"In France, we have freedom of creation, artistic freedom.\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3813, \"end\": 3819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993994315534153, \"rank\": 0.0004581123210912417, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are lucky in France to live in a free country.\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3884, \"end\": 3890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993994315534153, \"rank\": 0.0004581123210912417, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not have any specific messages that I wanted to deliver.\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In France, we are republic, we have the right to love whom we want, we have the right not to be worshippers, we have a lot of rights in France, and this is what I wanted to convey.\\\"\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 4162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3984, \"end\": 3990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993994315534153, \"rank\": 0.0004581123210912417, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4117, \"end\": 4123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9993994315534153, \"rank\": 0.0004581123210912417, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not everyone was offended by the performance, with some, such as Le Filip, the winner ofDrag Race Franceseason three, praising the artistic vision.\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought it would be a five-minute drag event with queer representation.\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was amazed,\\\" Le Filip told theAssociated Press.\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It started with Lady Gaga, then we had drag queens, a huge rave, and a fire in the sky.\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4455, \"end\": 4464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt like a crowning all over again.\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am proud to see my friends and queer people on the world stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Full Housealum Jodie Sweetin also took to her Instagram Story todefendthe performance, reposting a video explaining its connection to\\u00a0the Greek God Dionysus.\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4650, \"end\": 4663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Sweetin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jodie Sweetin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Sweetin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Sweetin\"}, {\"begin\": 4681, \"end\": 4696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Instagram Story\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagr